      "date": "2011-09-14 10:50:15.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4: Verified\n\nrecovery-mds-scale (FLAVOR=OSS) survived after running 2 hours (OSS failed over 6 times): https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/a49e7752-debe-11e0-9909-52540025f9af",
